across racial boundaries

00:45:02.100 --> 00:45:05.666
and are, in fact,
these social depression

00:45:05.666 --> 00:45:06.915
mechanisms like student loans.

00:45:08.220 --> 00:45:10.990
I mean, you've got a generation
